messages.message: Did this issue get resolved, I'm running into similar issues
I don't think so - it is a mypy complaint so I am assuming somehow it got slipped during premerge and post-merge tests?
Btw don't you see this error when make test in api-server-apps?

I was having errors in `api-server` that looked very similar to the ones you had in `api-server-apps`, then I took two steps: 1. `cd tools/devtools && make update-python`  2. Recompile all services locally.

After those steps the errors went away
Oh I see, thanks for the instructions, likely I have some old stuff running on my machine then
